<p sourcefile="manual/tuto1.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36" sourceendlinenumber="37"><img src="image1.jpg" alt="" sourcefile="manual/tuto1.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36" sourceendlinenumber="36">
